// J1.5, V1.1.3 Litefunction SetCookie(cookieName,cookieValue,nDays) {   var today = new Date();   var expire = new Date();   if (nDays==null || nDays==0) nDays=1;   expire.setTime(today.getTime() + 3600000*24*nDays);   document.cookie = cookieName+"="+escape(cookieValue) + ";expires="+expire.toGMTString()+"; path=/";   document.getElementById("cookieMessageContainer").style.display="none";      var href = window.location.href;   if (href.indexOf('?') == -1)   {      href = href+"?jjj="+Date.now();   } else   {      href = href+"&jjj="+Date.now();   }   window.location.href=href;}
